    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, the mechanical engagement is unparalleled. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable compression and rebound. Proactive maintenance includes documented rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the high-strung valvetrain remains robust. The exterior shows minor road wear consistent with spirited use, but the undercarriage remains clean with no signs of fluid seepage from the oil pan or differential seals.",
